00:24:35,575 --> 00:24:37,375
Meow! Treasure discovered in the next episode!

417
00:24:37,375 --> 00:24:38,775
How many servings of broiled eel on rice will I be able to eat?

418
00:24:38,775 --> 00:24:40,070
One-track mind.

